{"title": "Aqua Dream", "summary": "Underwater Effect Projector", "body": "Night light projector for babies with moving waves and fishes that glow on the walls and ceiling. Available with a variety of soothing songs and different intensities of light. This plush is ideal for creating a peaceful atmosphere in the bedroom.\n\n\n*2018*\n*sources : pabobo.com*\n[vimeo=714450981]\n[lp=Aquadream (2).jpg]\n\n[lp=Aquadream (4).jpg]\n\n**&&Prototype&&**\n\n[sp=QQ 20180816142449.jpg][sp=Tortue Proto trim.jpg][sp=QQ\u56fe\u724720180816115715.jpg]\n\n[lp=Aquadream (8).jpg]", "image": "Aquadream Cover.jpg", "id": 14}